translations: 无称号的；无标题的；无权利的

sentences.sentence: The full-length feature, as yet untitled, will include interviews plus footage of their live gigs.
sentences.translation: 仍未取名的未删节版的特辑将包括访谈及现场演唱会的片段。

sentences.sentence: Relativity's still-untitled Snow White film, starring Lily Collins as Snow and Julia Roberts as the Evil Queen, is scheduled to be released on March 16.
sentences.translation: 由莉莉·柯林斯饰演白雪公主，茱莉亚·罗伯茨饰演邪恶的皇后，Relativity 公司尚未命名的《白雪公主》电影计划于3月16日上映。

sentences.sentence: A blank form is created and you can see a new section called Untitled (form).
sentences.translation: 这就创建了一个空表单，您可以看到一个名为Untitled (Form)的新区域。
